FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780503064
OL,3,CFormer defence secretary calls for a
OL,4,Cnew review into Chinook crash
OL,6,FSir Liam Fox, who has been working
OL,7,Fwith the Chinook Justice Campaign,
OL,8,Fsaid new evidence suggested the
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence and RAF may have
OL,10,Fmisled two previous inquiries.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, he delivered a letter to
OL,13,FNumber 10 alongside families of the
OL,14,Fvictims, exactly 32 years after the
OL,15,Fdisaster, demanding an investigation
OL,16,Finto the exact cause of the tragedy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780503064
OL,3,CFormer defence secretary calls for a
OL,4,Cnew review into Chinook crash
OL,6,FAfter he had handed in the letter, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "We want there to be an overview
OL,8,Fof the whole of tragedy, not just the
OL,9,Fimmediate cause of the crash, which
OL,10,Fwas looked into, or the pilots'
OL,11,Fresponsibility, and they obviously
OL,12,Fwere cleared.
OL,14,F"But what was the sequence of events
OL,15,Fthat led up to this? We want Sir Keir
OL,16,Fto set up a mechanism of looking into
OL,17,Fthe whole issue with people who will
OL,18,Fbe qualified to look at all the data.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780503064
OL,3,CFormer defence secretary calls for a
OL,4,Cnew review into Chinook crash
OL,6,F"We want the inquiry to be guaranteed
OL,7,Faccess to all the information that we
OL,8,Frequire, so that we can produce for
OL,9,Fonce a complete narrative that sets
OL,10,Fout, in detail, all the decision-
OL,11,Fmaking points and how they were taken.
OL,13,F"The families feel that they have
OL,14,Fnever been given the whole story at
OL,15,Fany one point, that bits of it have
OL,16,Fbeen looked into. And what they want
OL,17,Fis truth, and they want closure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780503064
OL,3,CFormer defence secretary calls for a
OL,4,Cnew review into Chinook crash
OL,6,FDes Conroy, who's father was killed in
OL,7,Fthe tragedy, said: "32 years ago my
OL,8,Ffather dropped me off to the bus to go
OL,9,Fto work before going to his own work
OL,10,Fand that is the last time I saw him.
OL,12,F"For Liam Fox to come out and deliver
OL,13,Fa letter to the Government, to the
OL,14,FPrime Minister, we believe that is
OL,15,Fhuge for our campaign.
OL,17,F"We do believe justice is round the
OL,18,Fcorner for us."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
